// ARM Template: Web App + SQL Database + Key Vault + App Insights
// Deploy: az deployment group create --resource-group $RG --template-file webapp-sql-arm.json --parameters appName=myapp sqlAdminPassword=MyPass123!
//
// NOTE: Rename to .json and remove these comment lines before deploying
// ARM templates do not support comments in standard JSON
//
// Parameters:
//   appName:           Application name (3-20 chars)
//   environment:       dev | staging | prod
//   location:          Azure region (default: resource group location)
//   sqlAdminPassword:  SQL admin password (secure)
//   appServiceSkuName: B1 | S1 | P1v3 etc.
//
// Resources created:
//   - Log Analytics Workspace
//   - Application Insights
//   - Key Vault (RBAC-enabled)
//   - Storage Account
//   - SQL Server + Database
//   - App Service Plan (Linux)
//   - Web App (Node.js 18) with Managed Identity
//   - RBAC: Web App → Key Vault Secrets User
//
// Outputs:
//   webAppUrl, webAppName, sqlServerFqdn, keyVaultName, appInsightsConnectionString
